Fields.Name: id

Fields.Name: campaignName
Fields.Description: The name of the Campaign.

Fields.Name: maximizeReach
Fields.Description: Reach as many unique users as possible in your intended audience.

Fields.Name: maximizeLtvIncrementalReach
Fields.Description: The goal is to reach as many users as possible beyond those who have already reached on Linear TV.

Fields.Name: cpcInAdvertiserCurrency
Fields.Description: The Cost Per Click goal (in the Advertiser currency).

Fields.Name: ctrInPercent
Fields.Description: The Click Through Rate goal (in percent), for example, 1 = 1% (1 in 100).

Fields.Name: nielsenOTPInPercent
Fields.Description: The Nielsen On Target Percentage goal (in percent), for example, 1 = 1% (1 in 100).

Fields.Name: cpaInAdvertiserCurrency
Fields.Description: The Cost Per Acquisition goal (in the Advertiser currency).

Fields.Name: returnOnAdSpendPercent
Fields.Description: The Return on Ad Spend goal (in percent of ad spend).

Fields.Name: vcrInPercent
Fields.Description: The Video Completion Rate goal (in percent), for example, 1 = 1% (1 in 100).

Fields.Name: viewabilityInPercent
Fields.Description: The Viewability goal (in percent), for example, 1 = 1% (1 in 100).

Fields.Name: vcpmInAdvertiserCurrency
Fields.Description: The Estimated Viewable Cost Per Mille (thousand) goal (in the Advertiser currency).

Fields.Name: cpcvInAdvertiserCurrency
Fields.Description: Cost Per Completed View goal (in the Advertiser currency).

CustomTypes.Name: CampaignCreationInput
CustomTypes.Description: Schema with required fields for creating a new campaign

Fields.Name: advertiserId
Fields.Description: The platform ID of the advertiser that owns this Campaign.

Fields.Name: campaignName
Fields.Description: The name of the Campaign.

Fields.Name: campaignFlights
Fields.Description: The List of flights associated with the Campaign.

Fields.Name: startDateInclusiveUTC
Fields.Description: The date and time (in UTC) when the campaign flight is to start spending.

Fields.Name: endDateExclusiveUTC
Fields.Description: The date and time (in UTC) when the campaign flight is to stop spending if it has not yet exhausted its budget. To create or update a campaign flight, you may not set this property value to a date in the past.

Fields.Name: budgetInAdvertiserCurrency
Fields.Description: The maximum amount the campaign flight may spend. This must be in the currency of the advertiser that owns the campaign.

Fields.Name: budgetInImpressions
Fields.Description: The maximum amount of impressions the campaign flight should buy.

Fields.Name: dailyTargetInAdvertiserCurrency
Fields.Description: The total amount the campaign flight should spend in a single day, if possible. If you do not want to limit the daily spend, you may set it to null. This must be in the currency of the advertiser that owns the campaign.

Fields.Name: dailyTargetInImpressions
Fields.Description: The total amount of impressions the campaign flight should buy in a single day, if possible. If you do not want to limit the daily impressions, you may set it to null.
